{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Legalise the attachment of a small trailer to a mobility scooter",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I want the government to legalise the attachment of a small trailer to a mobility scooter. When I go shopping I am severely limited on how much I can fit in the basket on my mobility scooter. Being able to attach a small trailer, similar to one for a bicycle, would really enhance my ability to shop.",
